# Keep the Docker build context minimal. Two images build from this repo:
#   Dockerfile      -> the Track 2 submission (COPYs requirements.txt + src/)
#   Dockerfile.web  -> the hosted web demo   (also COPYs web_demo/)
# web_demo/ is therefore NOT ignored, but it never lands in the submission
# image because that Dockerfile simply doesn't COPY it.
# .env and .venv must never reach the build context.
.git
.gitignore
.env
.venv/
venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.vscode/
.claude/
docs/
output/
eval/
scripts/
scratch_videos/
submission_assets/
input/
README.md
.env.example
.dockerignore
Dockerfile
Dockerfile.web
